msgctxt "84_Fashionable Businesswoman"
msgid "Hey, when's that sale at the underground mall?"
msgstr "Oye, ¿Cuándo empieza esa promoción del Mall Subterraneo?"

msgctxt "96_Stylish Businesswoman"
msgid "Not anytime soon as far as I know. Didn't you say you were going to wait until stuff went on clearance?"
msgstr "No será pronto, que yo sepa. ¿No dijiste que irías cuando todo esté en liquidación?"

msgctxt "108_Fashionable Businesswoman"
msgid "But everything I want will be gone by then, especially that shirt and those boots! You remember the ones. You know what, screw the sale, I've gotta get over there!"
msgstr "Pero todo lo que quiero se habrá ido para entonces, ¡especialmente esa camisa y esas botas! Te acuerdas de ellos. ¡Sabes qué, al diablo con la venta, tengo que ir allí!"

